<br>
OR OR this one(People still fall for this one!)... Send out emails that you are paying money for people to stuff envelopes, $1 - 3 each make it sound realll good!! You will supply them the addresses, stamps, product to stuff and envelopes. When they pay the $30 &quot;registration&quot; fee you simply send them a mail with an envelope, and enclose $2 for stuffing it And a bunch of leaflets trying to get more money out of them ROFL!<br>
<br>
OR have 2 people in EC, One OOCing for a NEEDED quest item(insert rare 2sp item here) will trade EBOOTS for it, Spam zone for 2 hours or so(must be a rare item, like somthing off some goofy easy mob in a corner of a unused zone..Like Kerra Isle)). Now 30 minutes later on another char in an ajacent zone(with other char in EC still auctioning)auction WTS (the crap rare item here) for 5k!<br>
<br>
Person goes hmm.. EBOOTS FOR 5k!!!! wow!<br>
<br>
Lots of scams out there, BASICLY trust noone, Don;t put items in trade window to 'show' people, Don't buy trash for 5k because somone is supposidly trading eboots for it.<br>
